        {
          "text": "<https://stackoverflow.com/questions/73178041/xgboost-fit-vs-xgboost-train>\n\n읽어보시면 좋을 거 같습니다!",
          "user": "U041HMY5ZNX",
          "user_name": "전병웅",
          "timestamp": "1669292507.226059",
          "is_bot": false,
